  "name": "Send order confirmation from Shopify order and send to CRM",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Send order confirmation from Shopify order and send to CRM",
  "category": "Communication",
  "tags": [
    "n8n 2000 workflows",
    "slack",
